
pa_ppx_unique Version 8.04.01
-----------------------------

* [09 May 2026]

  * update source to be compat with new camlp5 8.04.01, OCaml 5.4.0

    OCaml 5.4 introduces labeled-tuples.  Some code here was
    incompatible, but wasn't even used.  Deleted it.

  * Change version-numbering of pa_ppx_unique so it matches that of
    Camlp5, since it is almost always the case that a new version of
    Camlp5 requires a new version of pa_ppx's base infra, and when
    it's new syntax, changes to the various derivers to support that
    new syntax.


